# Build context hygiene for the API/Worker images (context = repo root).
# Keep the context small and never ship build artifacts, tests, IDE files, the
# SPA source, or any local secret-bearing config into the image.
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
.git/
.github/
client/
docs/
tests/
**/*.user
**/TestResults/
# Local/dev config overlays must never enter the image (secrets come from the
# environment at run time — 11 §5). The base appsettings.json (no secrets) is fine.
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.*.local.json
.env
.env.*
